        {
            "title": "基石藥業折讓6.95%配股集資10.58億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">基石藥業(02616)公布，擬配售1.18億股集資約10.58億元；配股價8.97元，較該股昨收市9.64元折讓約6.95%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：基石藥業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250402_FI_source-web_02616-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：基石藥業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250402_FI_source-web_02616-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：基石藥業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價9.734元比較，配股價則折讓7.85%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司估計，集資淨額約10.53億元，約90%用於與公司「管線2.0」中的資產相關進一步研發；其餘款項於適當時用於其他一般公司用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15874211-%e5%9f%ba%e7%9f%b3%e8%97%a5%e6%a5%ad%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%936-95%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%8710-58%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
